What you need to know:

Even though the resumption of football is still in doubt, Ochola has warned fans against buying fake Gor Mahia merchandise that have since flooded the marketThe official added that in the past, the club has lost a lot of revenue because of individuals who sell branded club merchandise without the secretariat's consentOchola also revealed that the club's operations will be centralised at Finance House as part of concerted efforts to professionalise the club